<section
  style="position:relative; display:flex; flex-direction:column; overflow:hidden; min-height:100vh; padding:48px 64px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#06363A 0%,#08444A 55%,#063036 100%);"
>
  <div
    class="absolute pointer-events-none trama-texture"
    style="right:-180px; top:-40px; width:100%; height:100%; opacity:0.08; mix-blend-mode:soft-light; transform:scale(1.5);"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute pointer-events-none"
    style="left:-120px; bottom:-120px; width:620px; height:620px; background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(12,122,130,.22) 0%,transparent 70%); border-radius:50%;"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10">
    <h1
      style="max-width:420px; margin-top:110px; font-size:72px; font-weight:700; line-height:0.95; letter-spacing:-2px; color:#FFF;"
    >
      Donde el talento se <br />vuelve <span style="color:#0C7A82;">trama.</span
      >
    </h1>
    <p
      style="font-size:18px; line-height:30px; color:rgba(255,255,255,.88); margin-top:28px;"
    >
      Una nueva forma de conectar,<br />colaborar y crecer,<br />
      profesionalmente.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div
    style="margin-top:auto; height:auto; min-height:120px; border-radius:22px; padding:32px 40px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#006D75 0%,#0C7A82 100%); box-shadow:0 24px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.20);"
  >
    <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:24px; height:100%;">
      <div style="flex:1 1 180px; min-width:140px; text-align:center;">
        <svg
          width="56"
          height="56"
          style="display:block; margin:0 auto 12px;"
          fill="none"
          stroke="white"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
